 />\n而唔係日日頹廢做傷害人或者傷害自己既事<br />\n當社會上面既法律制裁唔到人<br />\n我覺得結果公義大過程序公義</blockquote><br />\n到你有份個時就唔係咁睇了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但俾佢捉得入去都係有問題啵<br />\n厄人保險公司 長期監等 吸毒 暴力傾向 屈人入罪既黑警 等等</blockquote><br />\n單向審判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f46ed28929ac6312772fc231a3a4cb301712d7","tid":306592,"uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:34:18.000Z","msg":"由第4集開始d 機器越整越大舊<br />\n你老味唔好話自己砌lego 咁砌<br />\n搵人砌都一萬個漏洞啦，重要每次一秒起好<br />\n越睇越痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09e93a8ac57bb1849b5842573b9ea96564bf589","tid":306592,"uid":100292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:35:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"18ad7fbb7a3b24090a6d28baef83dcb93a0b0d7b","tid":306592,"uid":100292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:35:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1022ca97687268a3f2ff055e9e08b6de4ba82fe7","tid":306592,"uid":60206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:38:13.000Z","msg":"第一集真係中學睇過到而家都仲記得<br />\n個結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737364d63df8deccc1b2dafab586c7da364bf497","tid":306592,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:06:48.000Z","msg":"條橋work既 <br />\n將一啲恐怖血腥遊戲<br />\n用唔珍惜生命黎包裝 <br />\n<br />\n第一集：精彩<br />\n第二集：唔錯<br />\n第三集：好心完鳩左佢啦 <br />\n<br />\n第四至七集：屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n恐懼鬥室出名在<br />\n佈局 連結 血腥 <br />\n<br />\n後尾得返血腥<br />\n仲要死拖爛拖回憶又回憶 <br />\n根本就係電影界既火影"},{"pid":"6b89550abc3ceb90ad9d2c40cd4c8e523bdad7de","tid":306592,"uid":56086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:12:34.000Z","msg":"最記得最尾個集有lin