lass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a7734299993b3564c33b467fc01c7191f56eee","tid":306592,"uid":38601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T23:54:58.000Z","msg":"睇過頭三集，其實頭三集側重嘅嘢已經唔同<br />\n第一集係推理+扭橋<br />\n第二集係人性遊戲<br />\n第三集係血腥<br />\n頭兩集各有各精彩，但第三集已經開始唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f493b46a7a2a7872120564de29643aba7be1e6e7","tid":306592,"uid":58008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T00:34:25.000Z","msg":"去到最後一集收尾手法唔錯<br />\n因為玩左成7集 佢都搵到位配合返前幾集<br />\nend得咁好"},{"pid":"a76ec817283e7e0365a9cdaa50a30afae2c51abb","tid":306592,"uid":18265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T00:38:03.000Z","msg":"第一集個醫生唔拍，搞到要改劇本，去到最後嗰集先出返嚟"},{"pid":"118e3090742fd6c2fa88625bcb1bfff65e8e2de3","tid":306592,"uid":18265,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T00:38:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一集個醫生唔拍，搞到要改劇本，醫生去到最後嗰集先出返嚟</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a12b621355a35d4b2a8fc704a9b1f9bf83a5da69","tid":306592,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T00:40:07.000Z","msg":"好似已經好多年前<br />\n七年前有3D上不過我得15歲唔入得場。。。<br />\n估唔到而家仲有人講<br />\n乜有8咩？<br />\n我連秋生失眠都無睇。。。好鍾意睇血腥野"},{"pid":"0d80984567ab4831780b5824103042dc23607ffe","tid":306592,"uid":87134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T01:01:07.000Z","msg":"一至三真係神戲<br />\n我個人覺得3&gt;2&gt;1<br />\n<br />\n第四集開始用個名呃人入場<br />\n睇到最後一集真係好失望<br />\n原本喺第三集完咗佢就可以名流青史<br />\n<br />\n仲要有好多人都唔識欣賞套戲<br />\n我成日同朋友講saw好睇<br />\n大部分以為我講緊夠血腥所以好睇<br />\n有啲仲夠膽話好鍾意睇<br />\n跟住係咁推薦其他戲比我話同saw差唔多<br />\n點知成套戲陣係無內容嘅血腥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab8e5ef7683ddf3b2c015c4f7b5cd3bd13de92e0","tid":306592,"uid":87134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T01:04:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇過頭三集，其實頭三集側重嘅嘢已經唔同<br />\n第一集係推理+扭橋<br />\n第二集係人性遊戲<br />\n第三集係血腥<br />\n頭兩集各有各精彩，但第三集已經開始唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實第三集佢係一開始已經test緊個女人，但係fake啲觀眾係test緊個醫生，我自己覺得個劇情編排最好係第三集喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27e9ef3854fcaefc21ecc855e74bc2f67fdbb00","tid":306592,"uid":87134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T01:05:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇過頭三集，其實頭三集側重嘅嘢已經唔同<br />\n第一集係推理+扭橋<br />\n第二集係人性遊戲<br />\n第三集係血腥<br />\n頭兩集各有各精彩，但第三集已經開始唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實第三集佢係一開始已經test緊<span style=\"color: red;\">amanda</span>，但係fake啲觀眾係test緊個醫生，我自己覺得個劇情編排最好係第三集喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3914a16e9d1db581f65c67dd2b98a71a79d9919d","tid":306592,"uid":45650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T01:10:24.000Z","msg":"第一集真係好神<br />\n<br />\n記得入戲院睇, 睇完個結局我同d fd個咀係O撚到合唔埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c6fa5c5088afd9f759f84fab92754c5fe949fd","tid":306592,"uid":45749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T01:16:54.000Z","msg":"第一集係神到好多日本漫畫都改篇 黑白熊 搜狼<br />\n<br />\n有一集講D遊戲每一關都要死一個人 但其實識合作玩係一個人都唔使死<br />\n但係人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf65c98055108ce95bb15d938f8c1b54fcc27469","tid":306592,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T01:24:03.000Z","msg":"全部睇晒 <br />\n1，2好正<br />\n之後純睇血腥尖叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82be39a8f972e883fcc65a76655903a4fb8dcf20","tid":306592,"uid":100292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T01:27:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01157058cd0a11d5d756fb54c52744a4129b202c","tid":306592,"uid":55453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite